{"data":[{"name":"114:1","price":"（使徒*よ、）言え。「私は人々の主*に、ご加護を乞う、","arabic":"قُلۡ أَعُوذُ بِرَبِّ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6231,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"qul aʿūdhu birabbi al-nāsi ","translations":["Say","I seek refuge","in (the) Lord","(of) mankind","(1)"],"transliterationArr":["qul","aʿūdhu","birabbi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,330],[2,330,1230],[3,1230,2050],[4,2050,6085]]}},{"name":"114:2","price":"人々の王、","arabic":"مَلِكِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6232,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"maliki al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) King","(of) mankind","(2)"],"transliterationArr":["maliki","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,640],[2,640,5205]]}},{"name":"114:3","price":"（真に崇拝*されるべき唯一の存在である、）人々の神¹に、","arabic":"إِلَٰهِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6233,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　「神」については、雌牛章１３３の訳注を参照。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"ilāhi al-nāsi ","translations":["(The) God","(of) mankind","(3)"],"transliterationArr":["ilāhi","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,840],[2,840,5295]]}},{"name":"114:4","price":"頻りに身を潜ませて囁きかける者¹（シャイターン*）の悪から。","arabic":"مِن شَرِّ ٱلۡوَسۡوَاسِ ٱلۡخَنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6234,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　シャイターン*は不注意な時には囁きかけてくるが、アッラー*が想起されると「身を潜めてしまう」（ムヤッサル６０４頁参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"min sharri al-waswāsi al-khanāsi ","translations":["From","(the) evil","(of) the whisperer","the one who withdraws","(4)"],"transliterationArr":["min","sharri","al-waswāsi","al-khanāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,400],[2,400,2119],[3,2119,3389],[4,3389,7914]]}},{"name":"114:5","price":"（それは、）人々の胸に（悪を）囁きかける、","arabic":"ٱلَّذِي يُوَسۡوِسُ فِي صُدُورِ ٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6235,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"alladhī yuwaswisu fī ṣudūri al-nāsi ","translations":["The one who","whispers","in","(the) breasts","(of) mankind","(5)"],"transliterationArr":["alladhī","yuwaswisu","fī","ṣudūri","al-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,1140],[2,1140,2130],[3,2130,2510],[4,2510,3420],[5,3420,7865]]}},{"name":"114:6","price":"ジン*と人々である」。¹","arabic":"مِنَ ٱلۡجِنَّةِ وَٱلنَّاسِ","category":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas"],"ayahNumber":6236,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"１　家畜章１１２も参照。尚、人間のシャイターン*の「囁き」とは、同情的な忠告者を装（よそお）って、ジン*のシャイターン*が囁くようなことを、忠告の形で胸に訴（うった）え かけること（アッ＝シャウカーニー５：７０８参照）。","lang":"ja","meta":{"transliteration":"mina al-jinati wal-nāsi ","translations":["From","the jinn","and men","(6)"],"transliterationArr":["mina","al-jinati","wal-nāsi",null],"verseTiming":[[1,0,380],[2,380,2610],[3,2610,8185]]}}],"chapter":["114 (An-Nas)","An-Nas","Surah An-Nas","Chapter An-Nas","Nas","Surah Nas","Chapter Nas","An Nas","Surah An Nas","Chapter An Nas","Surah 114","Chapter 114","Mankind","الناس"],"version":{"key":"japanese_saeedsato","direction":"ltr","language_iso_code":"ja","version":"1.0.10","last_update":1709035504,"title":"Japanese translation - Saeed Sato","description":"Translation of the Quran meanings into Japanese by Saeed Sato. printed in 1440 H."}}